title: Med Board Review
description:
AAFP Family Medicine Board Review Self-Study Packages
Developed by and for family physicians, this interactive learning package features an evidence-based review of everything you need to pass the ABFM Board exam. Recorded from the popular AAFP Family Medicine Board Review ExpressTM Live Course. Choose the package that's right for you!
Earn up to 38.75 AAFP Prescribed credits through this CME activity.
